(2) If any person contravenes any provision of subsection (1), he shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable on conviction to imprisonment for six months, or to a fine not exceeding fifteen thousand penalty units, or to both: Provided that no person, other than a proprietor, editor, master printer or publisher, shall be liable to be convicted under this section.
